msgstr "El indicador de contenido es obligatorio."

#: assets/js/admin.js
msgid "Please select a Template to continue."
msgstr "Selecciona una plantilla para continuar."

#: assets/js/admin.js
msgid "Are you sure you want to delete this structure?"
